rows.label: qst201609_msg0001
rows.name:
Now, the concert is finally
here, mo! Nanakoori-san,
are you ready, mo?

rows.label: qst201609_msg0003
rows.name: Nanakoori?

rows.label: qst201609_msg0004
rows.name:
What's wrong, mo? Is
your tummy hurting, mo?

rows.label: qst201609_msg0005
rows.name:
...No, it's not that... ...But
I don't think I can do it.

rows.label: qst201609_msg0006
rows.name:
It seems she's unwell
from being too nervous.

rows.label: qst201609_msg0007
rows.name:
This is terrible, mo?! She can't
perform at the concert, mo!

rows.label: qst201609_msg0008
rows.name:
No, there's still some time
until the concert. Let's calm
Nanakoori down before then.

rows.label: qst201609_msg0009
rows.name:
When Tora is like this, eating his
favorite food calms him down, mo.

rows.label: qst201609_msg0010
rows.name:
He eats lots and lots
of Tasty Sausages, mo!

rows.label: qst201609_msg0011
rows.name:
That sounds like it would
cause heartburn...

rows.label: qst201609_msg0012
rows.name:
However, it would be a distraction,
so I think it's a good idea.

rows.label: qst201609_msg0013
rows.name:
Then, let's have Nanakoori
eat her favorite food to
help her calm down.

rows.label: qst201609_msg0014
rows.name:
Nanakoori-san, what's your
favorite food, mo? I'll
bring it right away, mo!

rows.label: qst201609_msg0015
rows.name:
Huh? I can't think of
anything so suddenly...

rows.label: qst201609_msg0016
rows.name:
Is there anything you want to eat?
Just say whatever comes to mind.

rows.label: qst201609_msg0017
rows.name:
U-Um... I saw some Champ's
Churros in front of the playhouse,
and I'd like to try one.

rows.label: qst201609_msg0018
rows.name:
Could I have ten, including
some for Kumarin...?

rows.label: qst201609_msg0019
rows.name:
Kumarin is a big eater, mo... But
I'll go buy them right away, mo!

rows.label: qst201609_msg0020
rows.name:
Until you all get back, Teetapz will
entertain the waiting audience with
his charming conversation skills, mo.
